## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **clomipramine Anafranil 1989** = first FDA OCD — TCA serotonin-rich. 1980s 까지 OCD 가 "psychotherapy only" 였던 era 종료 → pharmacotherapy paradigm 시작. quantum-VQE 의 SERT + NET + H1 multi-target binding 직접 fit.
2. **SSRI 4총사 (fluoxetine 1994 + fluvoxamine 1994 + sertraline 1996 + paroxetine 1996)** = OCD 1L 표준 — clomipramine 의 anticholinergic + cardiotoxic 부작용 회피. SERT selective binding 이 OCD CSTC circuit 의 5-HT 결핍 hypothesis 와 fit.
3. **DBS Reclaim Medtronic 2009 HDE** = first FDA OCD 장치 — anterior limb internal capsule + NAcc 표적. treatment-resistant OCD (Y-BOCS ≥30 + 5+ failed pharmacotherapy + CBT/ERP) 환자 대상. quantum-VQE direct fit 없음 — circuit-level intervention.
4. **Deep TMS BrainsWay 2018** = first FDA OCD TMS — dmPFC + ACC 표적. DBS 보다 non-invasive — outpatient 가능. CSTC hyperactivity 의 cortical modulation paradigm.
5. **glutamate paradigm (riluzole + troriluzole + memantine + NAC + ketamine + esketamine 2010s+)** = OCD 의 "5-HT only" hypothesis 종료 → glutamate hyperactivity (CSTC) 가 next paradigm. troriluzole BioHaven Phase 2/3 + 만성 ASD trial. quantum-VQE 의 NMDA-NR2B + mGluR + EAAT 직접 fit.
6. **psilocybin + lysergamide 2020s+** = 5-HT2A psychedelic OCD research revival. small open-label studies + Phase 2 진행. cross-substance_use + ptsd_anxiety_specific.
7. **NAC + memantine + riluzole augment** = treatment-resistant OCD (TR-OCD) 의 "off-label augment" paradigm. SSRI + SGA augment 후 next-line. evidence base 가 small RCT 수준.
8. **PANDAS + PANS pediatric autoimmune** = pediatric OCD 의 sudden-onset autoimmune subtype. 만성 strep + autoantibody (cross-pediatric_rare + autoimmune). IVIG + plasmapheresis + 만성 antibiotic prophylaxis. quantum-VQE direct fit 없음 — immunology axis.
9. **CBT + ERP (exposure response prevention)** = OCD non-pharm 1L — pharma 보다 evidence stronger 일 수 있음 (Y-BOCS reduction). 만성 chronic + 만성 long-term maintenance. digital therapeutics (cross-digital_therapeutics) revival 가능.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, OCD 임상 의미 한정. troriluzole BioHaven Phase 2/3 readout 가 next milestone.

